es to > 700 for the most\nluminous starbursts at z ~ 2.5. With this amount of extinction, the optical\nmagnitude of a starburst having fv(7.7 um) of 1 mJy should be V ~ 25.6.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Jun 2009 14:55:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Oct 2009 14:39:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
